## 8.logicalNeg(x)
 01NN!=00x=01x 10<br />xsignXsignx1xsign0x0**positive overflow** Tmax + x x>00 -->1positive overflow  negative overflow[undefined behavior](http://port70.net/~nsz/c/c11/n1570.html#3.4.3p3)
```cpp
/* 
 * logicalNeg - implement the ! operator, using all of 
 *              the legal operators except !
 *   Examples: logicalNeg(3) = 0, logi'calNeg(0) = 1
 *   Legal ops: ~ & ^ | + << >>
 *   Max ops: 12
 *   Rating: 4 
 */
int logicalNeg(int x) {
  int Tmin = 1<<31;
  int Tmax = ~Tmin;
  int signX = ((x&Tmin)>>31) & 0x1;
  return (signX^0x1) & ((((x + Tmax)>>31)&0x1)^0x1);
}
```
